Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果七海的温柔是真实的话
